“Obama should target it and use a drone or something.”
Mike Huckabee, a Baptist minister, former governor of Arkansas and a possible presidential candidate, did not apologize.
“Anyone in the government who leaked the information is guilty of treason and anything other than execution would be too kind a punishment,” he said.
It’s not like you’re going to have to do that.
